List of extents for case study regions

Source: R/data_extent_list.R
extent_list.Rd

This object contains bounding boxes (latitudes and longitudes) for key study regions used in the refugia analysis. These can be used with terra::ext() for vizualisation.

Usage

extent_list

Format

An object of class list of length 4.

Source

Custom defined by project team

Details

Available extents:

  • Monterey Bay: monterey_bay

  • Fort Bragg: fort_bragg

  • Channel Islands: channel_islands

  • San Francisco: san_francisco

Examples

extent_list
#> $monterey_bay
#>   xmin   xmax   ymin   ymax 
#> -122.3 -121.5   36.4   37.1 
#> 
#> $fort_bragg
#>   xmin   xmax   ymin   ymax 
#> -124.3 -123.5   39.1   39.7 
#> 
#> $channel_islands
#>    xmin    xmax    ymin    ymax 
#> -120.50 -119.40   33.80   34.15 
#> 
#> $san_francisco
#>   xmin   xmax   ymin   ymax 
#> -123.5 -121.9   37.3   38.5 
#>
